article.headline: Wells scores 16, McNeese downs Texas A&M-Commerce 77-51

images.name: Texas A&M Commerce Lions vs. McNeese Cowboys: Game Highlights
images.caption: Texas A&M Commerce Lions vs. McNeese Cowboys: Game Highlights

article.linkText: Wells scores 16, McNeese downs Texas A&M-Commerce 77-51
article.story: LAKE CHARLES, La. -- — Shahada Wells' 16 points helped McNeese defeat Texas A&M-Commerce 77-51 on Monday night. Wells also had six rebounds for the Cowboys (20-3, 9-1 Southland Conference). Mike Saunders Jr. made all eight of his free throws and scored 14, adding five assists. DJ Richards sank three 3-pointers and scored 13. Tommie Lewis led the way for the Lions (8-15, 2-8) with 10 points and nine rebounds. Kwo Agwa had 10 points. for Texas A&M-Commerce. In addition, Kalen Williams finished with seven points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
